{"tid":2299700,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【民族復興】澳洲電視台：中国人甚麼都吃，唐朝的中国人常吃 曱 甴！","createTime":"2020-11-25T03:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T04:18:33.000Z","uid":293677,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b1b884f8d1774ec461d5c8c9c38b28fd6fd21255","tid":2299700,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><ins>「唐朝中國人常吃曱甴」 澳洲電視台捲辱華風波</ins></span><br />\n社會熱點 16:42 2020/11/23 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2805000/2809756/20201123_cockroach_v1_1024.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2805000%2F2809756%2F20201123_cockroach_v1_1024.png&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKG6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=f0c0fd38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2805000/2809756/20201123_cockroach_v1_1024.png</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">中國澳洲關係或再起波瀾。澳洲電視台兒童節目內容開中國歷史玩笑，稱中國人甚麼都吃，「唐朝的中國人更經常吃曱甴」，並用演員扮演武則天模擬進食曱甴（蟑螂）。節目雖由英國多年前製作，但最近在澳洲播出時也被指惡意醜華華人，涉嫌辱華，引起當地華人擔心加深澳洲國內種族歧視。</span><br />\n<br />\n澳洲廣播公司（ABC）近日播出兒童節目《糟糕歷史》（Horrible Histories），其中一集談論中國歷史，<span class=\"red\">稱中國人甚麼都吃，包括老鼠。</span><span class=\"red\">節目更用一名白人女演員化妝飾演女皇帝武則天，用筷子夾起一隻隻曱甴放入口裏</span>，旁邊的兩名白人男主持則表現出噁心的樣子，並說<span class=\"red\">「唐代中國人平常都吃這些」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n節目播出後，有澳洲華人表示已向ABC發出投訴。他們擔心這個節目會「教壞細路」，並可能在新冠肺炎疫情下，加劇澳洲國內種族主義者針對華人侮辱乃至人身攻擊的現象。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒報道，「武則天吃曱甴」一幕出現在《糟糕歷史》第6季，由英國廣播公司（BBC）於2015年首播。BBC最早於2009年開播《糟糕歷史》，以「惡搞」形式向兒童介紹有趣歷史，但前5季基本上講的基本上都是歐洲歷史，內容相對有考證，而第6季開始則更換了演職班子，並開始涉足亞洲國家歷史，被指缺乏考究和帶有傳統種族偏見。《糟糕歷史》另一集出場的孔子亦被指造型「很是尷尬」。<br />\n<br />\n《糟糕歷史》2014年也曾捲入種族風波「出事」。當年一集節目將英國19世紀女護士南丁格爾（Florence Nightingale）演繹成種族主義者，引起英國觀眾不滿。BBC解釋這只是開玩笑，但最終還是道歉並撤下節目。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2809756/%E3%80%8C%E5%94%90%E6%9C%9D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%B8%B8%E5%90%83%E6%9B%B1%E7%94%B4%E3%80%8D%20%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%8F%B0%E6%8D%B2%E8%BE%B1%E8%8F%AF%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2809756%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%2594%2590%25E6%259C%259D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E5%2590%2583%25E6%259B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B4%25E3%2580%258D%2520%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%258F%25B0%25E6%258D%25B2%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E8%258F%25AF%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKG6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=6cdf11b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2809756/%E3%80%8C%E5%94%90%E6%9C%9D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%B8%B8%E5%90%83%E6%9B%B1%E7%94%B4%E3%80%8D%20%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%8F%B0%E6%8D%B2%E8%BE%B1%E8%8F%AF%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"limegreen\">中国人唔食曱甴同老鼠？<br />\n邊個知呀？好難講喎<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"a58c4009edb4033ccf34b095f8be9e78765bc6c4","tid":2299700,"uid":360907,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:48:19.000Z","msg":"水曱甴係好多中國地區既名產喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔明邊度教壞"},{"pid":"ff133685efc760aa2b9316b5de594be41fa0266e","tid":2299700,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:48:51.000Z","msg":"[陳7入決賽啦] 明明香港人最鍾意投票，點解呢個投票會輸 (4)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2299625\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2299625</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n大家幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86f8de7e6f3823b86541025d298b9b8ee9acbe4","tid":2299700,"uid":299514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:50:59.000Z","msg":"有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181d46dacfa03091a525cf84cd7640be9f26383b","tid":2299700,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用老鼠肉整既羊肉串 好惹味！"},{"pid":"95839fbd74575c1da69d8bfe15ba6b671db7f718","tid":2299700,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"和味龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬼佬唔識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7809db3bc663b2a568fe3c00a4bc021c0443a3","tid":2299700,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf8c9c1b204044f53ec9b0670bc831bf2661975","tid":2299700,"uid":35205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:18:33.000Z","msg":"教育局澄清：ETV片段中是幽默敘事手法 與教師所犯之事性質不同<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2283475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2283475</a>"}]}